                <p data-translate="fuarSinglePage.description.p1">
                    Organized by KFA Fuarcılık A.Ş. and spearheaded by
                    the Bursa Chamber of Commerce and Industry, the Food Point Food Products and Technologies Fair
                    brings together the food industry's manufacturers, suppliers, and technology providers under one
                    roof.
                    <br />
                    <strong>
                        Food Point
                    </strong>
                    will be held simultaneously with the
                    <strong>
                        Horeca Bursa
                        Fair
                    </strong>
                    , organized by
                    <strong>
                        Network Fairs
                    </strong>
                    this year. Both fairs, under the
                    umbrella of
                    <strong>
                        “Bursa Food Fairs,”
                    </strong>
                    aim to create a strong synergy that appeals to
                    the entire sector by representing different areas of expertise.
                </p>
                <h6>
                    This major event, which will take place at the Bursa Fair Center, will host numerous
                    participants, primarily from the following sectors:
                </h6>
                <ul>
                    <li class="">
