                    </li>
                    <li class="">
                        • Snacks and beverage groups
                    </li>
                    <li class="">
                        • HORECA solutions and retail systems
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Food Point offers visitors the opportunity to closely examine innovations and cutting-edge
                    technologies in the sector, while also providing participating companies with opportunities to
                    establish new collaborations, increase brand awareness in domestic and international markets,
                    and communicate directly with their target audience.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>
                        Bursa Food Fairs
                    </strong>
                    is a strategic organization that showcases Türkiye's
                    production and export strength in the food industry, supports sectoral collaborations, and aims
                    to make Bursa a hub in the food sector.
                </p>
